  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle and preheat the oven to 220&deg;C/ 200&deg;C (fan)/ 425&deg;F/ Gas 7</p>\r\n<p>Peel the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>&nbsp;and cut into batons</p>\r\n<p>Cut the <strong>courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>&nbsp;into batons</p>\r\n<p>Cut the <strong>r</strong><strong>ed onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>&nbsp;into quarters (keeping the peel on)</p>\r\n<p>Cut the <strong>red pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>&nbsp;in half</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Place the <strong>vegetables</strong> on a baking tray (use two if necessary) and drizzle with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>olive oil</strong></p>\r\n<p>Season&nbsp;with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Put the tray in the oven for 20 min or until the vegetables are tender with a slight bite</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>bulgur</strong> to a pot with plenty of <strong>salted boiled water</strong> over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Cook for 8-10 min or until tender with a slight bite, then drain and return to the pot</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> with half the <strong>honey</strong>, half the <strong>harissa paste</strong> and 2 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>olive oil</strong></p>\r\n<p>Reserve the remaining <strong>honey</strong> and <strong>harissa</strong> for the next step</p>\r\n<p>Season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> &ndash; this is your <strong>harissa dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Combine the remaining <strong>harissa paste</strong> with the remaining <strong>honey</strong> and the <strong>chopped garlic&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and mix well to combine &ndash; this is your <strong>honey harissa mixture</strong> for the next step</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/366_step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>feta</strong> evenly (for stuffing the pepper halves)</p>\r\n<p>Remove the <strong>vegetables</strong>&nbsp;from the oven&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Stuff the <strong>peppers</strong> with the <strong>feta</strong></p>\r\n<p>Transfer the cooked<strong> onions</strong> to a chopping board</p>\r\n<p>Spoon the <strong>honey harissa mixture</strong> over the <strong>carrots</strong> and <strong>courgettes</strong></p>",
